name: FilterDatetime
description: Represents how to filter a date when filtering on values.

properties.name: date
properties.description: The date in ISO8601 format used to filter data.

properties.name: specificity
properties.description: How specific the date should be used to keep data. For example, if the date is 2005-04-02 and the specifity is set to "month", the filter operation will keep all rows with a date in the month of april 2009.
